SAMSUNG FASCINATE APP MODS
==========================

BASE VERSION: EI20

REQUIRED TOOLS: apktool

FRAMEWORKS USED IN DECOMPILE (apktool -if <framework>):
    EH09 framework-res.apk (deodexed)
    EH09 twframework-res.apk (deodexed)

SERVICES.JAR
============

- Changed default LiveWallpaper to com.android.wallpaper/.nexus.NexusWallpaper

FRAMEWORK.JAR
=============

- Modified for Verizon Wireless
- Modified for addition of Reboot and Recovery power menu options

FRAMEWORK-RES.APK
=================

- NOTE: Was decompiled with "apktool d --keep-broken-res"
- Modified for addition of Reboot and Recovery power menu options
- Use CRT screen-off animation (mod courtesy of nitsuj17)

ANDROID.POLICY.JAR
==================

- Modified for addition of Reboot and Recovery power menu options
- Add back in support for Puzzle lockscreen
- Stop animation services (samsungani/bootanim) at the same time

BROWSER.APK
===========

- Removed all default bookmarks
- Set default home page to "about:blank"

CAMERA.APK
==========

- Update MMS settings
- Remap power button to trigger the shutter rather than locking the controls

JOBMANAGER.APK
==============

- Don't hide Google Maps, Magic Smoke Live Wallpaper or Dual Clock widget from Task Manager
- Hide many well-known launchers from Task Manager

MMS.APK
=======

- Set mms_config.xml options from ED05 Froyo Mms.apk as well as some settings ccampos784 used
- Port MmsConfig.smali from USCC EH09 version

MUSICPLAYER.APK
===============

- Localize some strings for US English

SETTINGS.APK
============

- Add "Unlock Screen" settings back to "Display Settings"

SYSTEMUI.APK
============

- NOTE: Was decompiled with "apktool d -r" due to problem linking back to twframework-res.apk
- Remove full battery notification

TOUCHWIZ30LAUNCHER.APK
======================

- Modified default shortcut and widget layouts



